[In light of these events, it is worth rereading "BSE policy - USA:
change considered, 20050418.1094" and related posts. This is the 1st
autocthonous US BSE diagnosis in some 388 000 samples tested. What
the true risk is is a matter of some heated debate, unfortunately. -
Mod.MHJ]
